Singer Paolo Nutini has announced the dates for his rescheduled Glasgow gigs. Paolo Nutini to play rescheduled Glasgow Hydro gigs Singer Paolo Nutini has announced the dates for his rescheduled Glasgow gigs.
The Paisley-born musician cancelled two shows at the SSE Hydro on Monday and Tuesday after being diagnosed with severe tonsillitis. 
Monday's postponed show will now take place on Friday 9 January 2015, with the second show rescheduled for Saturday 10 January 2015.
Tickets for the original shows remain valid.
 